Package: phiprotect
Type: Package
Title: Protected Health Information Detection and Anonymization
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given="Ronald", family="Levitin", email="rlevitin@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A comprehensive toolkit for detecting, classifying, and anonymizing
    Protected Health Information (PHI) in healthcare datasets. Implements
    risk-based classification (HIGH/MEDIUM/LOW) following HIPAA guidelines and
    provides statistical disclosure control methods appropriate for each risk
    level. Supports both in-memory data frames and database tables with
    zero-exposure introspection capabilities.
